data.title: CV Sample 1
data.meta_description: CV Sample 1 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Asif Raza is seeking an internship in brand management and provides his contact information and objective. He summarizes his skills as being punctual, hardworking, a team player with strong communication skills both written and oral. He is currently studying for his MBA at GIFT University where he is captain of the cricket team and has an 85% overall percentage with a 3.2 CGPA. Previously, he obtained a B.Sc from Punjab University where he was on the intercollegiate cricket team and had a first division with 65% marks. For projects, he conducted a marketing plan for Nestle juices identifying trends and strategies and performed a customer satisfaction survey for GIFT University analyzing determinants of satisfaction and providing recommendations
